Honey, ain't nobody done
nothing to spite you.

1287
01:57:46,984 --> 01:57:48,515
Yes, indeed.

1288
01:57:50,303 --> 01:57:54,089
She an ugly little girl, too.
That little pug nose...

1289
01:57:54,522 --> 01:57:57,955
I hope she grow out of it.
- You need to stop that.

1290
01:57:58,537 --> 01:57:59,802
You know that ain't right.

1291
01:57:59,903 --> 01:58:02,861
Don't you think she look a little
like Louis around the mouth?

1292
01:58:02,912 --> 01:58:07,427
I think she look just like you.
- Like me?! - Yes.

1293
01:58:07,488 --> 01:58:10,684
So, you need to stop
talking about her.

1294
01:58:11,656 --> 01:58:14,866
Let me look at her again
then real good...

1295
01:58:17,480 --> 01:58:20,011
She do look a little bit like me.

1296
